Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:05.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The star of a show is usually charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.91,0:00:07.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However, the same could be said for the culprit or victim...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.70,0:00:09.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Today's case is about a misunderstood dying message.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:11.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Work hard on today's case, Officer Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:13.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Solve the case involving "Smiling Peace"!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:14.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seeing through to the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:16.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I look like a child, but have the intellect of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:18.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\3a&H64&\be1\fad(0,450)}My name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:52.22,Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:54.14,Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.14,0:01:55.19,Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You'll catch a cold doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:02.65,Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A-ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:08.27,Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's a man who fainted!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:11.45,Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}His head is bleeding a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:13.90,Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.82,Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:19.25,Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The ambulance is so slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.25,0:02:21.96,Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why aren't they here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:24.80,Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The station isn't far from the bus stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.53,0:02:29.05,Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If they're not coming, then I'll go there myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.38,0:02:45.94,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:47.78,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The man who found the victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:50.57,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}disappeared after he called for an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:53.57,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The first one to find the victim disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:57.04,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So that means he escaped right after calling 911.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:00.43,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:03.25,Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:05.58,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:08.09,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The person who found the victim and then ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:11.89,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8}I didn't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:13.47,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8}I just wanted to get an ambulance quicker...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:16.72,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An ambulance, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:18.19,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There was no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:21.75,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The victim was dead long before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:24.11,Dialogue,Blue person,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:28.03,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was an immediate death from being hit in the back of his head by a blunt object.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:29.57,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry to take up your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:30.57,Dialogue,Blue person,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:39.07,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Doesn't it seem odd to call for an ambulance unnecessarily?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:39.58,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:43.17,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't know whether he was dead or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:44.55,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:46.13,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing else!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:49.63,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's Hiromatsu Hiroshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:54.05,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Looks like he's a hot-headed policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:55.07,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:57.45,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Address, name, age, and occupation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:03:58.89,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Write down every detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:05.51,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's Hiromatsu Hiroshi no matter which way you read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:06.73,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What a weird name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:10.65,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't help that.  It's my real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:14.32,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Occupation, comedian?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:15.16,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've never seen you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:18.04,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, I'm not that famous, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:20.58,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If this random man was the first to find the victim...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:22.29,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The victim...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:24.83,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Have I seen this hand gesture before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:25.91,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:28.00,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.80,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A smile and peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:32.34,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What could the meaning behind this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:33.88,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, you're finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:34.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:35.62,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:39.10,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is something wrong...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:43.21,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:44.31,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Iwaii Hirono!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:44.69,Dialogue,Hirono,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:50.04,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Find out as much as you can on this man for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:51.92,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:52.86,Dialogue,Men,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.03,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did I write something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:04.21,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Officer Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:06.38,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm Takagi from the metropolitan area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:08.17,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takagi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.38,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hiromatsu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:13.26,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Officer Sakurada from the Eastern side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:14.89,Dialogue,Policeman,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You know this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:19.57,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He helped me with a robbery case in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.57,0:05:20.80,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:24.77,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I found the victim during my routine jogging.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:26.94,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you're the first one to discover the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:29.32,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Only "found", eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:30.28,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:34.91,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It seems like the officer considers that man a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:35.78,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Conan-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:39.16,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyway, Sakurada-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:41.12,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why do you suspect Hiromatsu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:44.16,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Suspecting the first one who found the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:45.37,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}is the first law of investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:48.09,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm not the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:52.91,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know Hiromatsu-kun. It couldn't be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:56.09,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The reason why I'm suspecting him is because...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:05:59.85,Dialogue,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8}I'm the one,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:03.39,Dialogue,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8}who received your message at Yasunaga Agency, Yasunaga Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:06.28,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Officer Sakurada from the Eastern police headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:06.85,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:09.62,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're Mizuhara Ryoji-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:11.50,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're always in TV dramas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:12.86,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh yeah, that actor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:15.17,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Mizuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:19.78,Dialogue,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8}Okubo was Mizuhara's manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:21.29,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okubo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:24.29,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We believe Okubo Iwao-san was the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:27.39,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please verify the body for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:30.54,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:32.75,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:35.26,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A "V" sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:36.91,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Is it him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:38.25,Dialogue,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:40.64,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's my manager, Okubo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:43.23,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hiromatsu-kun, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.27,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How should I say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:47.10,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You know this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:50.11,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We live in the same apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:53.45,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,500)}I see, so that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:58.41,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}On the phone, you said Okubo-san worked very late yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:02.16,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He was in my room just a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:04.78,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He visited very late last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:09.64,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We mainly discussed my future in the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:10.92,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We talked until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:16.17,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Afterwards, he left at 4:30 AM,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:18.74,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}to catch the first bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:23.14,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okubo-san left Mizuhara-san's room,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:26.73,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}for the bus stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:33.77,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He died at 4:40 AM,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:36.90,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}only 10 minutes after he left Mizuhara-san's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:39.52,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We haven't found the weapon yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:42.40,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but looking at the wound, it was most likely a blunt object.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:45.83,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then, 20 minutes later, at 5:00 AM,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:48.18,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you found the body during your jog.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:49.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:53.17,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Both of you live at the 4th Street Apartments.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:55.27,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The bus stop is here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:57.52,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and the station is just ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:08:00.88,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's something like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.62,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takagi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:04.86,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I never got to finish my explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.86,0:08:08.81,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll tell you why I suspect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:11.98,Dialogue,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This man killed Okubo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:13.39,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:14.94,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I said it's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:18.58,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}First of all, you were the first to find the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.24,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When a culprit commits murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:23.74,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}he doesn't know if he left anything at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:26.99,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If he pretends to be the first to find the body,however,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:29.45,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}no matter what he left behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:32.49,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}he could just say it's from when he found the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.54,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:35.14,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Second,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:37.88,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you went to the station to get an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:39.88,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}People usually wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:44.89,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Most likely, you had an ulterior motive for going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:48.06,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:49.68,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:54.06,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is Sakurada.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:56.27,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You found the weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:58.07,Dialogue,Blue guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.78,Dialogue,Blue guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a steel pipe with traces of hair on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:04.40,Dialogue,Blue guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and blood that hasn't had time to dry yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:05.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:06.28,Dialogue,Blue guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We found it under...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:08.10,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kamitakada Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:09.23,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:10.38,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:13.28,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kamitakada Bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:17.42,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's between the murder scene and the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:18.67,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:24.22,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you didn't go to the station to get an ambulance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:30.31,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but to dispose of the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.39,0:09:31.85,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:34.39,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why would I do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:36.88,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Of course, we can speculate on your motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:41.78,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Although you're a comedian, you're not very popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:47.94,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you begged your manager, Okubo-san, who visits Mizuhara-san frequently,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:51.55,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}to find a job for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:54.66,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He didn't even consider it, so you got angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:56.54,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:10:00.29,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Most importantly, is the victim's dying message,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:02.13,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}which clearly indicates that you're the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:04.05,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Dying message?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:05.51,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:11.45,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's the strange way Okubo-san died with a smile on his face and forming a "V" sign with his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:16.02,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's the dying message?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:19.23,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In other words, the name of the culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.28,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:29.28,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}"Smiling Peace"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:32.50,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I knew you were a comedian,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:34.51,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but this is your stage name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:36.29,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, that doesn't mean I'm the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:37.79,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please believe me, Takagi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:40.50,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, do you have an alibi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:41.91,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alibi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:46.27,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If the murder happened at 4:40 AM,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:47.59,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was still in my room at that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:53.10,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I left a little before five to go jogging!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:56.10,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If we could only prove that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:11:01.52,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How do you find proof of that for someone who lives alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:05.58,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh yeah, after Okubo-san left,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:08.49,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I set my alarm clock before going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:14.20,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That was when I heard the toilet flush next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:17.91,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That was at 4:40 AM right, Mizuhara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:18.71,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:21.83,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your alibi checks out, Hiromatsu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:22.42,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:24.92,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What is with his expression?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:28.93,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Um, can I go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:34.22,Dialogue,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You must be shocked, having this happen to your manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:36.27,Dialogue,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mizuhara can leave now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:40.45,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Although I want to do a survey again,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:41.27,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}that's it for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:46.69,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}May I also leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:51.66,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I still need you to tell me the circumstances in which you found the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:54.28,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, yeah. That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:00.37,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.17,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Got it! Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:06.67,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hate to break it to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:08.67,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but your alibi has just been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:13.75,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After I began suspecting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:18.03,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I asked others to search for the traces you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:24.37,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You appeared in the video in front of the store on Third Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:26.78,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The time was 4:30 AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:30.28,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.64,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I lied!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:36.12,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I left the apartment and started running before 4:30 AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.49,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hiromatsu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:42.00,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, if I told you the truth, I'd become the main suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:44.00,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you couldn't help lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:46.84,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So that's why you had a weird expression earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:50.80,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mizuhara-san was either confused or just heard something,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.82,0:12:53.80,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't think he would lie for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:59.60,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you kept what Mizuhara-san heard a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:01.00,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, that's what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:04.52,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You shouldn't lie, even if you'll be suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:07.11,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please come to the police station with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:08.53,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hiromatsu Hiroshi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.53,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No. "Smiling Peace"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:14.82,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takagi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:23.00,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sakurada-san only took the weapon and motive into consideration!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:26.04,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The main problem is that dying message.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:28.17,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Smiling Peace"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:30.05,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To think that was his stage name...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:33.43,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How did Okubo-san know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:35.75,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've never heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:38.76,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've only heard of the man living next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:41.96,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Although I don't see Mizuhara-san anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:45.06,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}he used to be on TV a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:48.82,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He was a handsome guy who always kept his cool and never smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:53.32,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't leave Hiromatsu-kun alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:56.03,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll attend his interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.03,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}"Smiling Peace"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:00.03,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A smiling face and a "V" sign...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.33,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Smiling face...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:04.04,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:09.50,Dialogue,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.25,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Edogawa Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:14.59,Dialogue,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, Conan-kun, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:17.64,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Officer Takagi wanted me to come and ask you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:22.64,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"What did Okubo-san talk to\NMizuhara-san about yesterday?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:26.02,Dialogue,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was about the future of his career.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.02,0:14:29.52,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah! He asked me to ask what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:34.90,Dialogue,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The future of his career is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.45,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:41.91,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The mystery behind that dying message is solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:44.44,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:48.88,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}...the true culprit is that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:55.42,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yasunaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:57.55,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The president of the agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:15:01.94,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, she told me to tell you something that might be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.26,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:06.60,Flashback,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The future of his career is in his smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:09.06,Flashback,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:14.94,Flashback,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Mizuhara Ryoji is famous for always keeping his cool and never smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:17.98,Flashback,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That path has come to a dead end now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:24.99,Flashback,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So, Okubo-san suggested that he try to change his image to that of a smiling person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:32.42,Flashback,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Since he's very charming when he smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:35.42,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}"Change his image to that of a smiling person?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:39.47,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, but that request just came out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:41.26,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's probably hard for Mizuhara-san to accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:45.52,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not only hard to accept, but it might even infuriate him as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:50.27,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's hard to change your behavior like that so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.11,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:58.11,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And she said that Okubo-san really cares about Mizuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:02.29,Flashback,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Okubo-san was really sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:05.83,Flashback,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It was diagnosed that he only had 6 months left to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:08.83,Flashback,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He should have been in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:11.28,Flashback,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But, no matter what, he wanted turn Mizuhara,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:12.68,Flashback,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}his first client,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:14.92,Flashback,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}into a famous star again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:17.38,Flashback,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Even his life didn't matter to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:19.88,Flashback,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Compared to Mizuhara, nothing else mattered to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:22.34,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}More than his own life...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:25.43,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If it's like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.43,0:16:27.64,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}then I understand the meaning of the dying message.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:28.89,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:32.35,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes. If I'm right,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:34.23,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}this case is a really sad turn of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:38.61,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's right. This isn't a typical case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:43.86,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:45.95,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why is everyone gathered at the crime scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.52,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sakurada-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:51.97,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The culprit behind Okubo-san's death isn't Hiromatsu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:55.21,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rather, the true culprit is someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:59.71,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}First, the culprit disposed of the weapon and fled from the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:01.47,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, which way did the culprit go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:06.22,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The weapon was found under the\NKamitakada Bridge, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:11.73,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However, that doesn't mean the culprit went there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:14.60,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In fact, he could have gone this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.19,0:17:19.78,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So the culprit was just trying to turn the police's attention away from himself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:21.99,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What a childish trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:23.88,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:26.89,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now we know the culprit lives here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:27.89,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-le-le?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:32.18,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Doesn't Mizuhara-san also live in this apartment complex?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:33.21,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:36.28,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Second, is the alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:40.25,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Most likely, this murder was unplanned,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:43.80,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so the culprit didn't prepare one beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:46.26,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rather, he thought of a really air-tight one later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:50.72,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You lied to create an alibi so you\Nwouldn't be under suspicion, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:54.13,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The culprit took advantage of that lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:55.48,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:59.73,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who's the one person who benefited from your lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:04.45,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right, it's Mizuhara Ryoji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:09.45,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're the one who killed Okubo-san, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:13.66,Flashback,Mizuhara (flashback),0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That was when I heard the toilet flush next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:17.58,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}You weren't confused and didn't mishear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:23.67,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Based on that statement, we thought you had been in your room that whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:29.43,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But yesterday, Okubo-san suggested that you change your image.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:32.45,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He told you that you needed to show your smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:36.48,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But for you, being the "cool guy who never smiles",
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:38.94,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you didn't agree with that suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:42.44,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You were probably thinking something like,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:49.02,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"If things continue like this, I'll be forced to change myself. What a joke!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:50.20,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:54.47,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How could I, Mizuhara Ryoji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:57.21,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How could I smile like a silly little kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:19:00.33,Dialogue,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mizuhara, how could you do that to Okubo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:05.76,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This morning, you followed Okubo-san from your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:20.44,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:25.44,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How do you explain the odd position that he died in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.19,0:19:27.30,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just like you thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:30.91,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}it was his dying message.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:35.45,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However, it wasn't "smiling peace", but a smile and a "V" sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:38.61,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's Okubo-san's final testament,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:41.38,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}as Mizuhara-san's manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:46.38,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What Okubo-san wanted to say is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:50.42,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Mizuhara, smile, always try to smile."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:52.85,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Your smile is the best."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:19:58.89,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:00.58,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:03.62,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why would he encourage the person who killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.57,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's a good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:12.91,Dialogue,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And it's that Okubo-san cared about Mizuhara a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:17.08,Dialogue,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even in the final moments of his life,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:20.87,Dialogue,Yukiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}he was still thinking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:27.15,Dialogue,Mizuhara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okubo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:34.26,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okubo-san was thinking of you until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:37.93,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Repent for your crime and try to start over, Mizuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:43.86,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We'll talk about the details at the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:47.23,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sakurada-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.19,0:20:50.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hiromatsu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:52.61,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please apologize to Hiromatsu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:58.41,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Apologize to him for accusing him of being the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:21:01.16,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All he did was lie about the alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.62,0:21:03.88,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's certainly not right to lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:08.07,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but you need to hold those who force others to lie accountable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:09.17,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:12.04,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Am I wrong, Sakurada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:15.89,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Suspecting the first one who found the body may be the primary law of investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:20.64,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, it could also lead to the wrong conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:24.31,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This could be a lesson for us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:28.40,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's absolutely unacceptable for police officers to be biased.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.77,0:21:30.07,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Absolutely unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.74,0:21:32.86,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:35.03,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:37.38,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:38.19,Dialogue,Sakurada,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:42.95,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you very much,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:44.04,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takagi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.48,0:21:45.88,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.00,0:21:48.54,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}You were great, {\alphaFF}Officer Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:50.42,Thoughts,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}You were great, Officer Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.72,0:23:21.26,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But, when you said the smile and the "V" sign led to the culprit,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.37,0:23:23.85,Dialogue,Hiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I thought it was the end for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.32,0:23:27.77,Dialogue,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was an unreasonable explanation from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.86,0:23:31.77,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, I thought that Okubo-san wouldn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.77,0:23:34.48,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the comedian called "Smiling Peace."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.78,0:23:37.95,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not even the professional managers?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.95,0:23:40.78,Dialogue,Conan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Am I really {\i1}that{\i0} unknown?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.99,0:23:44.29,Thoughts,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Continue to try your best, Hiromatsu-kun!
